  "detailed_description": "Are you ready to face the duality of the World?<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2534550/extras/883a27574536d60a0aa07df7aaa2963e.avif?t=1722955483\" width=506 height=100 /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2534550/extras/c1270e27466e4a8cfdc6f4b9bd7074ae.webp?t=1722955483\" width=506 height=32 /></span><br><br>In this roguelike, twin-stick shooter, the only way of preventing the world from<br>ending is by staying in a (toxic) relationship with the manifestation of Yin-Yang<br>itself!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2534550/extras/a6a253c7aea92ea8131d1e36ccc4d1a3.poster.avif?t=1722955483\" width=506 height=284 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2534550/extras/a6a253c7aea92ea8131d1e36ccc4d1a3.webm?t=1722955483\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2534550/extras/a6a253c7aea92ea8131d1e36ccc4d1a3.mp4?t=1722955483\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2534550/extras/76d9d7c5e714c0d5abe24e37d9947f73.webp?t=1722955483\" width=506 height=31 /></span><br><br>Monsters are approaching from the dark side! <br>Your evil nature is taking over, fight off the enemies and defend the Yin Yang! <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2534550/extras/a1b9fce4870372ac3197abcfc26afd56.poster.avif?t=1722955483\" width=506 height=284 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2534550/extras/a1b9fce4870372ac3197abcfc26afd56.webm?t=1722955483\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2534550/extras/a1b9fce4870372ac3197abcfc26afd56.mp4?t=1722955483\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2534550/extras/e3693b2637e783d3ff9ff3d815fbfaaa.webp?t=1722955483\" width=506 height=32 /></span><br><br>Unlock a whole Gallery of Weapons and Abilities through the achievements.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2534550/extras/e2a42818c24d744aa6e03d09f6c0526c.poster.avif?t=1722955483\" ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2534550/extras/e2a42818c24d744aa6e03d09f6c0526c.webm?t=1722955483\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2534550/extras/382614dc3947ff41b7971a6d60ff8dfe.webp?t=1722955483\" width=506 height=32 /></span><br><br>With more than 500 combinations of weapons, abilities, and effects, <br>endless replayability is not just a keyword.<br><br>In addition, you can master your game on 5 levels of difficulty.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2534550/extras/61ce49ea76257b2fb37840960f136069.gif?t=1722955483\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2534550/extras/61ce49ea76257b2fb37840960f136069.poster.avif?t=1722955483\" class=\"bb_img\" /></picture></span>",
